Package: covidR
Type: Package
Title: COVID-19 Scraping and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joshua N. Grant <grantjn@ornl.gov>
Maintainer: Joshua N. Grant <grantjn@ornl.gov>
Description: Contains scripts to collect data from State Department health sites
    or other reliable sources, import them into a database, and visualize a 
    timeseries of the data via a shiny interface.
